Description: THE PURPOSE OF THE SPONSORED PREPARATORY SCHOOL PROGRAM IS TO PROVIDE AN ENVIRONMENT THAT PREPARES THE PREP STUDENT ACADEMICALLY AND PHYSICAL FOR THE RIGORS OF THE UNITED STATES MERCHANT MARINE ACADEMY (USMMA). THE PREP SCHOOL MUST HAVE A YEAR-LONG DEVELOPMENTAL PROGRAM THAT QUALIFIES STUDENTS FOR ADMISSION TO THE ACADEMY AND PREPARES THEM FOR SUCCESS AS USMMA MIDSHIPMEN.
